  "reference_number": "RUS1326",
  "remarks": "\nVladimir BOGDANOV is the Chief Executive and Deputy Chairman of the Board of Directors of Surgutneftegaz, Russia’s fourth-largest oil producer. In his capacity as the CEO of Surgutneftegaz, BOGDANOV is or has been involved in obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia by working as a director or other manager of an entity which is carrying on business in a sector of strategic significance to the Government of Russia, namely the Russian energy sector. \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
